<br>
So I finished the code and I put up the rules that had most recently sort of been agreed on, overnight. I didn't realise I was writting a legal document, and I always thought (nievely yes) that any problems people had with the rules would come out right then. I was actually very surprized no one said a thing. I got lots of comments and corrections on the links page.<br>
<br>
Whatever or however I said it this is what was supposed to come through:<br>
<br>
The plane needs to be cleared. If you can't clear the whole plane (ok exception sky but you know what I mean) then you have no business reserving a whole plane. Yes we said 40 but in reality the reason for the 40 was to make absolutely sure you have enough to draw from to clear a plane, take however many you want more or less, invite friends but make no mistake you need to clear it. The exception to this would be when a god is up, in that case... yadda yadda epic guild... yadda yadda god loot etc.<br>
<br>
