<br>
If a guild is in trouble it has basically three options, as I see it anyway, they can try to stay within the 6 invites per tag rule and get help then from anyone and everyone, clear as far as they can and let someone know they left mobs up especially Maestro.  This is the best choice IMO. But be honest with yourselves and get help in the future, invite a guild to your alliance whatever.<br>
<br>
